Sentencas: Dense bismuth oxides stabilized with lanthanide dopants (delta-Bi2O3) are always used as interlayer for thin layer GDC (gadolinia-doped ceria) or YSZ (yttria-stabilized zirconia) electrolyte solid oxide fuel cell to improve the cell performance.
Titulo: High performance cathode-unsintered solid oxide fuel cell enhanced by porous Bi1.6Er0.4O3 (ESB) interlayer

Sentencas: Dense ESB (Bi1.6Er0.4O3) layer preparation needs special equipment or well synthesized nano-sized powders, which is not friendly for large scale and commercial application.
Titulo: High performance cathode-unsintered solid oxide fuel cell enhanced by porous Bi1.6Er0.4O3 (ESB) interlayer

Sentencas: In this paper, anode support unsintered cathode cell with porous ESB interlayer is prepared through simple screen print and its electrochemical performance is tested.
Titulo: High performance cathode-unsintered solid oxide fuel cell enhanced by porous Bi1.6Er0.4O3 (ESB) interlayer

Sentencas: No matter sintered or not, porous ESB interlayer lowers both the polarization resistance and ohmic resistance, and enhances cell performance, especially for the ohmic resistance of unsintered cells.
Titulo: High performance cathode-unsintered solid oxide fuel cell enhanced by porous Bi1.6Er0.4O3 (ESB) interlayer

Sentencas: The cell with ESB porous interlayer and SSC (Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-delta)-ESB unsintered cathode achieves a peak power density of 1.329 W cm(-2) at 700 degrees C, which is 1.61 times higher than that of the cell without ESB interlayer and 0.93 times higher than that of the sintered cell.
Titulo: High performance cathode-unsintered solid oxide fuel cell enhanced by porous Bi1.6Er0.4O3 (ESB) interlayer

Sentencas: However, the durability of porous ESB interlayer enhanced cells is not ideal and it should be improved in further works.
Titulo: High performance cathode-unsintered solid oxide fuel cell enhanced by porous Bi1.6Er0.4O3 (ESB) interlayer
